resources.string: Orbotpe chi anwei kɵmɵn ikpape internetyu mentra kenamarmɵ chine maramtik kɵn. Orbotpe, internet yu wammeran mentra lasrpitsɵsrkɵmɵntrappe Tor teik tɵka wetɵ ashmɵntrai isua marik kɵn, trek chippe chi wam merane esekawa ampumai imai purep ipik kɵn pɵrashmerayu ik pirau mupa kuin pɵrap. Torpe kan software kɵn mayaelai chi anwei kɵmɵ, incha chu puisrɵ, kape chu pasriksrɵpe, wam kerilan mu kɵpen wampikelɵ wetɵ ashmɵntrai purukupik kɵn, trek tɵwai chutɵ kucha maya misakwan aship pasrapik Estado teik wan purukupik kɵn, kan \"analisis de tráfico\" teik tɵka.

Orbotpe mayaelai kɵn, ikpe møi eshkailø tøkaik køn Tor, IPtProxy (Obfs4Proxy, Meek, Snowflake), Go-Tun2Socks and LibEvent. Kan VPN kelichai purɵrɵpik, kan Proxy HTTP (HTTPS puerto 8118yutɵ kepintrapik) srape kan proxy SOCKS (9050) Toryu kelichapik.
